        <updateDate>2009-01-13T20:31:10Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ Simple Savings Tax Relief Act of 2009 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to exclude from gross income up to $400 (twice such amount on a joint return) of interest income annually. Provides for an inflation adjustment to such exclusion amount beginning after 2010.]]></text>
      </summary>
